x4freetext: CH4 gas used as target and counting gas in ionization
chamber at a pressure of 200 mbar

x4codes.hlp: Ionization chamber

x4freetext: Multisampling ionization chamber (MUSIC)
filled with CH4 gas serving both as target and
counting gas. The anode of the detector was
subdivided into 18 strips, each subdivided into two
parts, which were used as a multiplicity filter.
Beamlike or fusion events have multiplicity one,
elastic and inelastic scattering produces
multiplicity two events that can easily be rejected
No uncertainties given
Compiled by S.H.
Data taken from fig. 2 of the reference,
waiting for data from author
